Drisc tools

INSTALL

Uncompress the archive in a directory then just type 

	make

(you need a working copy of Ocaml!)

USE

	parse xxx
	=> parses the assembler program in file xxx 

	drisc xxx [ssss]
	=> parses the assembler program in file xxx and executes ssss
	   instructions, dumping state (pc, mem, reg) after the 
	   execution of each Drisc instruction. In case ssss is omitted
	   1000 steps are performed (max)
